<D>__{my little stinker.}
<C>__{jeannie}
<D>__{my big stinker.}
<A>__{the background to this intimacy is enormously alive. the lead actress and the character actor laughing out loud. in the b.g., we see the audience filling out preview cards as the floor manager leans in to say:}
