<A>__{jeannie, shocked by her father's unprecedented sentiment, turns to face him and clamp a hand over his mouth so he will add no more lush and primal affection. having silenced him though, she finds that she has something of her own to say. she'd never tell it to her father, but she can't resist telling it to her acting coach.}
